Metadata.Title: No Spy
Metadata.Description: Our insider was killed last week. I managed to track down the killers. 5 of them are all in this hotel. We MUST avenge Leon, or else we're NOTHING! You must get in, get out, FAST. Twitch will be driving a boat to get you out of there, he won't wait long. Oh also, DONT CAUSE SUSPICIONS!
